---
title: "US23 — Create / like / comment on posts"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>SocialScreen / PostDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>CreateWorkoutSharePost · TogglePostLike · AddPostComment
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SocialGateway → Supabase
  A->>B: share a workout
  B->>C: createWorkoutSharePost(caption)
  C->>G: insert posts (kind=workout_share)
  A->>B: tap like / write comment
  B->>C: toggleLike(post) / addComment(text)
  C->>G: insert/delete post_likes · insert post_comments
  G-->>C: ok
  C-->>B: updated counts
  B-->>A: like + comment reflected
